USAGE:

1. cd ~/Library/Application\ Support/Textmate/Bundles
2. git clone git@github.com:dfltr/Galzroth.git Galzroth.tmbundle
3. Textmate -> Bundles -> Bundle Editor -> Reload Bundles
4. Hit CMD + S
   4a. Behold as trailing whitespace disappears into the infernal maw of Galzroth, Devourer of Whitespace
   4b. Make everyone you work with install this bundle
   4c. Enjoy your new life, free of whitespace diffs

FAQ:

Q: Why is this bundle called "Galzroth, Devourer of Whitespace"?
A: Because Stone Cold said so.